{"id":639659,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/苹果日报｜秋雨教会案：王怡狱中照曝光体态消瘦/","date":"2020-03-26T15:23:28Z","modified":"2020-03-26T15:23:28Z","title":"苹果日报｜秋雨教会案：王怡狱中照曝光体态消瘦目光深沉","content":"<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/PQDP5WZTJ5N2PCUW5AX5SXFJTY.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-639660\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/PQDP5WZTJ5N2PCUW5AX5SXFJTY.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/PQDP5WZTJ5N2PCUW5AX5SXFJTY.jpg 802w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/PQDP5WZTJ5N2PCUW5AX5SXFJTY-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/PQDP5WZTJ5N2PCUW5AX5SXFJTY-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>四川省成都市秋雨教会主任牧师王怡，2018年底被当局关押，去年底被以煽动颠覆国家政权罪和非法经营罪被判监9年，引来国际关注。王怡的狱中照近日曝光，可是他消瘦不少。</p>\n<p>在狱中的王怡明显比以往消瘦，目光深沉看着镜头；与他过往有着圆润脸庞比起来，分别甚大。这也是王怡自2018年底失踪后，外界首次看到他的样子。</p>\n<p>王怡是成都秋雨教会的牧师，他推动家庭教会公开化，谴责习近平暴政，坚持每年公开纪念六四。2018年12月9日，公安大规模拘捕秋雨教会会友，王怡牧师等逾50名弟兄姊妹、教会牧师助理及传道人李英强其后亦遭拘押；时至今年2月，秋雨教会仍有十多名教友被刑拘及指定居所监视居住。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Pastor <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WangYi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#WangYi</a> in prison, first seen since his arrest in Dec 2018.<br />The first portrait was done according to his photo before arrest. <br />Look how much weight he has lost in China‘s prison from the second photo !<br />Not hard to imagine the torture he experienced behind the red bars. <a href=\"https://t.co/pmh7fSiycD\">pic.twitter.com/pmh7fSiycD</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 巴丢草  Badiucao (@badiucao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/1242834131341303808?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 25, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"c5ZEpRtG6R\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/12/%e7%bb%b4%e6%9d%83%e7%bd%91%ef%bd%9c%e6%88%90%e9%83%bd%e7%a7%8b%e9%9b%a8%e6%95%99%e6%a1%88%e7%8e%8b%e6%80%a1%e7%89%a7%e5%b8%88%e8%a2%ab%e5%88%a4%e5%a4%84%e6%9c%89%e6%9c%9f%e5%be%92%e5%88%919%e5%b9%b4/\">维权网｜成都秋雨教案王怡牧师被判处有期徒刑9年</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《维权网｜成都秋雨教案王怡牧师被判处有期徒刑9年》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/12/%e7%bb%b4%e6%9d%83%e7%bd%91%ef%bd%9c%e6%88%90%e9%83%bd%e7%a7%8b%e9%9b%a8%e6%95%99%e6%a1%88%e7%8e%8b%e6%80%a1%e7%89%a7%e5%b8%88%e8%a2%ab%e5%88%a4%e5%a4%84%e6%9c%89%e6%9c%9f%e5%be%92%e5%88%919%e5%b9%b4/embed/#?secret=c5ZEpRtG6R\" data-secret=\"c5ZEpRtG6R\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"H55JdcVDKR\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/%e7%8e%8b%e6%80%a1-%e9%9d%a2%e5%af%b9%e9%80%bc%e8%bf%ab%ef%bc%8c%e6%88%91%e4%bc%9a%e6%80%8e%e4%b9%88%e5%81%9a/\">王怡 | 面对逼迫，我会怎么做</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《王怡 | 面对逼迫，我会怎么做》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/%e7%8e%8b%e6%80%a1-%e9%9d%a2%e5%af%b9%e9%80%bc%e8%bf%ab%ef%bc%8c%e6%88%91%e4%bc%9a%e6%80%8e%e4%b9%88%e5%81%9a/embed/#?secret=H55JdcVDKR\" data-secret=\"H55JdcVDKR\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"HKHfDE7p1Q\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/%e3%80%90cdtv%e3%80%91%e7%8e%8b%e6%80%a1%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%80%e6%97%a6%e6%8e%8c%e6%9d%83%e8%80%85%e5%85%ac%